snippet.title: Samurai Unicorn - Official Trailer | The Indie Horror Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Samurai Unicorn is an action horror game with retro graphics set in the sprawling megacity of Sydney3. Check out the creepy trailer to see some of the nightmarish enemies that await you in Samurai Unicorn. Samurai Unicorn will be available on PC.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
